room_title: Escape room "The Lost Tomb of Anubis " by Great Escape of Central Texas in Killeen
room_address: 4400 E. Central Texas Expy Killeen, TX 76543
room_description:
Your team are freshman archaeology students and while excavating an Egyptian tomb you discover a secret chamber.  The discovery of a lifetime EXCEPT the door closes behind you and you’re cut off from the outside world AND your teacher, the only one who knows anything about Egyptology.  Armed with only your wits and each other, you must find your way out before your air runs out and of course while battling the evil curses you’ve unleashed.

​
